POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/comment/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "topicId": 1,
  "body": "This is my comment on the topic.",
  "parentCommentId": null
}

### Create Reply to Comment (Authenticated)
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/comment/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "topicId": 1,
  "body": "This is a reply to a comment.",
  "parentCommentId": 1
}

### Update Comment (Authenticated)
PUT {{API_HostAddress}}/api/comment/update/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "body": "Updated comment text."
}

### Delete Comment (Authenticated)
DELETE {{API_HostAddress}}/api/comment/delete/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

